        Selling in Kelvin Grove 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Kelvin Grove's QUT precinct, Victoria Park access and two distinct property markets create a suburb where campaign strategy matters more than in most inner Brisbane locations. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
